;;-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
;;Browsers versus acid test
;;http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Comparison_of_web_browsers
;;by country 2012
;;http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-DM2ZE4UStV0/T5va382dWII/AAAAAAAAA9E/8ebMQKot9G0/s1600/popular.png
;;Market Share from W3Schools data (AWESOME)
;;http://www.axiis.org/examples/BrowserMarketShare.html
;;Browsers with layout engine
;;http://user-agent-string.info/list-of-ua
;;groupings in this db are by:
;; a) rendering engine
;; b) name (if rendering engine obscure)
;; c) hardware (if it constrains rendering engine)
;;the structure of this file is similar, but not identical, to an PHP ini file - changed
;;for fast manual editing
;;UA groups are listed in the approx order of the popularity of the platform
;;values can be a value, true, false, unknown
;;-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------


;;-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
;;google chrome beta
;;features at http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Google_Chrome
;;-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
